Reasoning: The paper discusses the development of an intelligent tutoring system that provides hints to students based on past student data. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of this system in supporting students in solving multi-step tasks, which is relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of this system in open-ended programming tasks, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
